OL,3,CCCTV shows moment car hits five-year-
OL,4,Cold girl and then drives away
OL,6,FThe suspected vehicle, a grey BMW,
OL,7,Fovertook another vehicle waiting at
OL,8,Fthe junction of Langham Way and Sloper
OL,9,FRoad. It then mounted the pavement,
OL,10,Fhitting a five-year-old girl, who was
OL,11,Freturning from the park with her
OL,12,Fmother and brother.
OL,14,FThe girl, who had been riding her
OL,15,Fscooter along the pavement, suffered
OL,16,Fminor injuries.
OL,18,FThe incident, occurred on Sunday, 24
OL,19,FMarch at around 5.50pm.
