OL,6,FIn a statement, a South Wales Police
OL,7,Fspokesperson said: "CCTV shows a
OL,8,Fspeeding car mount the pavement,
OL,9,Fcollide with a little girl, and drive
OL,10,Foff.
OL,12,F"Amazingly the little girl received
OL,13,Fonly minor injuries, but the incident
OL,14,Fwas understandably very frightening
OL,15,Ffor her and her family.
OL,17,F"Officers are appealing for the driver
OL,18,For anyone with information to please
OL,19,Fcontact South Wales Police."
